{"type":"message","id":"442ff510","parentId":"f99f4212","timestamp":"2026-03-24T08:26:46.955Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_58br4jkwpmz8_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5217\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2292\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 042615 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the critical next step for Phase 1, but there's no implementation yet to analyze the pulse logs for invariant/variant patterns. The theory is solid; we need the tool to test it.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"brisk-shore","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5217\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2292\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] the\r\n[mutation proposed] the\r\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 042615 - The TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the critical next step for Phase 1, but there's no implementation yet to analyze the pulse logs for invariant/variant patterns. The theory is solid; we need the tool to test it.\r\n","name":"pwsh C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774340806952}}
{"type":"message","id":"70f28dc4","parentId":"442ff510","timestamp":"2026-03-24T08:26:46.957Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_58br4jkwpmz8_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Pulse: 2026-03-24 042413\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\n\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me review the current state and determine a specific action to advance the goals.\r\n\r\nCurrent state:\r\n- Phase 0 and Phase 1 (architecture cross-analysis) are complete\r\n- Key insight: Compression and Causal Discovery are the same problem\r\n- Next action: TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) Experiment\r\n- Need to implement TIC classifier on pulse logs\r\n\r\nThe pending task is to implement the TIC experiment. This involves:\r\n1. Implementing TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files\r\n2. Measuring invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n3. Predicting next pulse content from invariants\r\n4. Validating against success criteria\r\n\r\nLooking at the notes, there's a recent pulse log: `pulse_2026-03-24 042319.md`\r\n\r\nA concrete action would be to:\r\n1. Check what pulse logs exist in the logs directory\r\n2. Create a script or begin implementing the TIC classifier\r\n\r\nLet me first check the logs directory to see what pulse logs exist, then implement a basic TIC classifier.\r\n\r\nI should look at:\r\n1. The logs directory structure\r\n2. The format of existing pulse logs\r\n3. Then create a TIC classifier script\r\n\r\nLet me write a PowerShell script that:\r\n1. Reads pulse logs\r\n2. Implements basic invariant/variant classification\r\n3. Makes predictions about next pulse content\r\n\r\nThis advances the pending TIC experiment goal.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next priority but requires implementing a classifier on pulse logs. I need to examine existing logs and build the classifier.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nCreate `tic/tic_classifier.ps1` - the TIC experiment implementation that reads pulse logs, classifies content as invariant (stable patterns) vs variant (novel changes), and validates against success criteria (>70% classification accuracy, >60% next-pulse prediction).\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # TIC Classifier - Temporal Invariance Compression Experiment\r\n# Tests hypothesis: Causal structure IS invariant structure\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$Lookback = 20,\r\n    [double]$Threshold = 0.6\r\n)\r\n\r\n$LogsDir = \"logs\"\r\n$OutputFile = \"tic/results.md\"\r\n\r\n# Gather pulse logs sorted by date\r\n$logs = Get-ChildItem \"$LogsDir/pulse_*.md\" | \r\n    Sort-Object Name | \r\n    Select-Object -Last $Lookback\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"TIC Classifier: Analyzing $($logs.Count) pulse logs\"\r\n\r\n# Extract content patterns from each log\r\nfunction Get-Patterns {\r\n    param($Content)\r\n    $patterns = @{\r\n        Goals = @()\r\n        Actions = @()\r\n        Findings = @()\r\n        Gaps = @()\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract goal mentions\r\n    if ($Content -match '(?m)^## (.+)$') {\r\n        $patterns.Goals = $matches[1]\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract action patterns\r\n    if ($Content -match '(?i)action:|### ACTION') {\r\n        $patterns.Actions = \"action_present\"\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract mutation patterns (file edits)\r\n    if ($Content -match '(?i)MUTATION|old_text|new_text') {\r\n        $patterns.Mutations = \"mutation_present\"\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract insight patterns\r\n    if ($Content -match '(?i)insight:|finding:|key') {\r\n        $patterns.Findings = \"finding_present\"\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Extract gap references\r\n    if ($Content -match '(?i)gap|decay|forgetting') {\r\n        $patterns.Gaps = \"gap_reference\"\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    return $patterns\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Classify each pulse\r\n$results = @()\r\nfor ($i = 0; $i -lt $logs.Count; $i++) {\r\n    $log = $logs[$i]\r\n    $content = Get-Content $log.FullName -Raw\r\n    $patterns = Get-Patterns $content\r\n    \r\n    $isInvariant = ($patterns.Actions -ne \"action_present\") -or\r\n                   ($patterns.Mutations -eq $null) -or\r\n                   ($patterns.Findings.Count -eq 0)\r\n    \r\n    $results += [PSCustomObject]@{\r\n        File = $log.Name\r\n        Patterns = $patterns\r\n        IsInvariant = $isInvariant\r\n        Content = $content\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Predict next pulse from invariants\r\n$invariants = $results | Where-Object { $_.IsInvariant }\r\n$variants = $results | Where-Object { -not $_.IsInvariant }\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"Invariants: $($invariants.Count), Variants: $($variants.Count)\"\r\n\r\n# Calculate invariant ratio\r\n$invariantRatio = if ($results.Count -gt 0) { \r\n    $invariants.Count / $results.Count \r\n} else { 0 }\r\n\r\n# Predict next pulse characteristics from invariant patterns\r\n$predictedNext = @{\r\n    LikelyActions = ($invariants.Patterns.Actions | Group-Object | Sort-Object Count -Descending | Select-Object -First 1).Name\r\n    CommonGoals = ($invariants.Patterns.Goals | Group-Object | Sort-Object Count -Descending | Select-Object -First 3).Name\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Validate prediction against actual next pulse\r\n$nextPulsePrediction = $null\r\nif ($logs.Count -ge 2) {\r\n    $lastLog = $logs[-1]\r\n    $lastContent = Get-Content $lastLog.FullName -Raw\r\n    $lastPatterns = Get-Patterns $lastContent\r\n    \r\n    $nextPulsePrediction = @{\r\n        HadAction = $lastPatterns.Actions -ne $null\r\n        HadMutation = $lastPatterns.Mutations -ne $null\r\n        Goals = $lastPatterns.Goals\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n# Calculate metrics\r\n$classificationAccuracy = $invariantRatio  # Placeholder -\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 04:24:51\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774340806955}}
